reviewText: Home video cameras record the outrageous, the uncensored and the unbelievably bizarre antics of dogs, cats, birds monkeys and many more. From exotic tourist destinations to city zoos, monkeys are always the center of attraction. From outsmarting their human cousins for a free meal to shocking onlookers with their naughty public behavior, these animal antics are uniquely entertaining. YOU'LL See - Turtles taking a time out for romance, A love struck parakeet courting the family dog and the randy rabbit attracted to a rooster. Warning: This program is intended for mature audiences only. Parental Discretion is advised.
